  searchResult

mock.onPost("/api/update/bookmarks").reply(request => {
  const bookmarkToUpdate = JSON.parse(request.data).obj

  searchResult.filter(i => {
    if (i.id === bookmarkToUpdate.id) {
      return (i.starred = !bookmarkToUpdate.starred)
    } else {
      return null
    }
  })
  return [200]
})
